column5: Does anyone know if Lew has moved into his new digs yet? I know it was supposed to be around early to mid February.  I was thinking of taking a drive over and welcoming him to the neighborhood.  Tom.
He must be in the midst of moving now, Tom.
Morning Tom, moving day is March 1st.
Don't know how their furniture shopping is going but I've upped my Leon's stock portfolio just in case. :-)
If I don't see you before then Lew, I will just look for the house with all the new empty Leon,s boxes out front...  Tom.
And the new truck, and the new boat, and the new tv .... seems to me his wife and dog should be gettin' real nervous.  JF
